 for RVM-inflation preserves the\nbasic structure of the original (and more phenomenological) RVM, as well as its\nmain advantages: namely, a mechanism for graceful exit and for generating a\nhuge amount of entropy capable of explaining the horizon problem. It also\npredicts axionic DM and the existence of mild dynamical Dark Energy (DE) of\nquintessence type in the present universe, both being \"living fossils\" of the\ninflationary stages of the cosmic evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Dec 2020 22:13:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-20"}
