climates. We summarize\nthese results and also compare ROCKE-3D to previously published simulations of\nthe inner edge that used a modified version of the NCAR CAM4 model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Dec 2020 22:57:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-17"}
