equency harmonics are enhanced due to the\nhigh-frequency modulations from the direct laser coupling with created pair\nplasmas.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Dec 2020 14:28:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-20"}
