ad: While the benefits of enforcing one-way foot traffic in\n(wide) walkways are unclear, changing the geometry of queues substantially\naffects disease transmission risks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Dec 2020 15:08:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Feb 2021 08:13:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 3 Nov 2021 09:27:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-04"}
