r to the thermographic measurement. The radiometric intensity depends on\ne.g. the angle of incidence of the thermographic measurement, which is now\nknown and can be used to narrow down the electrical conductivity of the\nmeasured object.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Dec 2020 06:01:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-22"}
